sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant APIServer as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as spark-operator-webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as spark-operator-controller<br/>ServiceAccount token
    participant Driver as Driver Pod<br/>spark-submit
    participant Executors as Executor Pods<br/>7078/TCP, 7079/TCP
    participant SparkUI as Spark UI<br/>4040/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: SparkApplication Submission

    User->>APIServer: POST SparkApplication CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / kubectl
    APIServer->>Webhook: POST /mutate-sparkapplication<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS (self-signed)
    Webhook-->>APIServer: Mutated SparkApplication<br/>(defaults applied)
    APIServer->>Webhook: POST /validate-sparkapplication<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS (self-signed)
    Webhook-->>APIServer: Validation result
    APIServer-->>User: SparkApplication created

    Note over Controller,Executors: Controller reconciliation loop

    Controller->>APIServer: Watch SparkApplication CRs<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    APIServer-->>Controller: SparkApplication event (New)
    Controller->>Driver: spark-submit (in-process)
    Controller->>APIServer: Create Driver Pod<br/>HTTPS/443

    APIServer->>Webhook: POST /mutate--v1-pod<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS
    Note over Webhook: 24-step mutation pipeline:<br/>volumes, env vars, ConfigMaps,<br/>ports, affinity, security context,<br/>sidecars, GPU, monitoring

    Webhook-->>APIServer: Mutated Pod spec

    Driver->>Executors: Spawn executors<br/>TCP/7078, 7079 (no encryption)
    Driver->>SparkUI: Expose Spark UI<br/>HTTP/4040

    Controller->>APIServer: Update status: Running<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Driver,Executors: Job execution

    Executors-->>Driver: Task results<br/>TCP (no encryption)
    Driver-->>Controller: Job completed (pod status)
    Controller->>APIServer: Update status: Completed<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: ScheduledSparkApplication

    User->>APIServer: POST ScheduledSparkApplication CR
    Note over Controller: Internal cron timer fires
    Controller->>APIServer: Create child SparkApplication<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    Note over Controller,Executors: Follows Flow 1 from webhook step

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: SparkConnect Server

    participant Client as Client Application
    participant ConnectSvc as SparkConnect Service<br/>15002/TCP

    Controller->>APIServer: Create Pod, Service, ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    Client->>ConnectSvc: Spark Connect protocol<br/>TCP/15002 (no encryption)
    ConnectSvc->>Executors: Execute queries<br/>TCP/7078, 7079

    Note over Prometheus: Monitoring

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 (no auth)
    Prometheus->>Webhook: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 (no auth)
